♪ YOU WERE MADE FOR HORIZONS

13:28.024 --> 13:30.548
♪ YOU'RE GONNA FLY AWAY

13:30.679 --> 13:33.073
♪ ONE DAY

13:35.162 --> 13:38.121
♪ LIKE A PHOENIX RISING

13:38.252 --> 13:41.124
♪ YEAH IT'S YOUR DESTINY

13:41.255 --> 13:44.736
♪ YOU'RE FATE TO FEEL THE THRILL

13:44.867 --> 13:47.435
♪ DARLING DON'T BE AFRAID

13:47.565 --> 13:50.351
♪ I KNOW THAT YOU HAVE THE STRENGTH

13:51.569 --> 13:53.658
♪ TO PUSH THE LIMITS

13:55.225 --> 13:57.793
♪ YOU ARE ONE OF THE BRAVE

13:57.924 --> 14:00.709
♪ NEVER COULD BE CONTAINED

14:00.840 --> 14:02.232
♪ OH

14:02.363 --> 14:04.844
♪ IVE GOTTA LEARN TO LET YOU GO

