14:15.898 --> 14:18.770
♪ WATCH YOU FROM THE DISTANCE

14:18.901 --> 14:21.338
♪ FROM THE DISTANCE

14:22.165 --> 14:25.734
♪ NEVER FELL SO PROUD

14:25.865 --> 14:28.476
♪ YOU'RE SOARING SO HIGH

14:29.129 --> 14:31.087
♪ HIGH IN THE SKY

14:32.915 --> 14:35.875
♪ NOW YOU TOUCH THE CLOUDS

14:36.919 --> 14:39.008
♪ YOU DON'T HAVE A LIMIT

14:39.966 --> 14:41.837
♪ HAVE A LIMIT

14:42.925 --> 14:46.059
♪ WAY BACK ON THE GROUND

14:46.668 --> 14:49.497
♪ I WATCH YOU FROM THE DISTANCE ♪

14:50.280 --> 14:52.152
♪ FROM DISTANCE

