♪ TILL I TURN BLUE

21:09.180 --> 21:11.226
♪ LETS GET BUSY

21:11.357 --> 21:13.837
♪ NOTHING STOPPING US

21:13.968 --> 21:16.753
♪ LISTEN TO ME

21:43.127 --> 21:45.304
♪ TAKE MY HAND

21:45.434 --> 21:47.915
♪ AND RUN AWAY WITH ME

