22:01.624 --> 22:03.104
♪ INTO ECSTASY

22:03.234 --> 22:04.888
♪ LET'S GET BUSY

22:05.019 --> 22:07.630
♪ NOTHING STOPPING US

22:07.761 --> 22:09.980
♪ LISTEN TO ME

22:27.998 --> 22:32.699
[CROWD NOISES]

22:39.575 --> 22:41.621
-ISN'T IT FABULOUS?
LOOK AT THE LUSTER.

22:41.751 --> 22:43.492
KIM, HOLD IT MORE
UP INTO THE LIGHT.

22:43.623 --> 22:44.928
-MOM.

22:45.059 --> 22:46.539
-WELL, IT'S A BEAUTIFUL
ENGAGEMENT RING.

22:46.669 --> 22:48.541
YOU SHOULD BE PROUD
TO SHOW IT OFF.

22:48.671 --> 22:50.064
-IT'S A LITTLE
LOOSE. I HAVEN'T HAD

22:50.194 --> 22:52.196
A CHANCE TO GET IT SIZED YET.

22:52.327 --> 22:54.634
-OH, THERE'S HARRY AND
SUSAN. LET'S GO SHOW THEM.

22:54.764 --> 22:56.200
EXCUSE US GIRLS.

23:07.647 --> 23:08.691
-AH, THERE YOU ARE.

23:09.953 --> 23:11.607
YOU REMEMBER BROWN GOODMAN?

23:12.478 --> 23:16.264
-HI SHAUNI, YOU'RE LOOKING
BEAUTIFUL AS ALWAYS.

23:17.352 --> 23:18.962
-THANK YOU.

23:19.093 --> 23:21.008
UM, DAD, CAN I SPEAK WITH
YOU FOR A MINUTE PLEASE.

23:22.357 --> 23:24.054
WILL YOU EXCUSE US?

23:24.185 --> 23:26.100
-ONLY IF YOU PROMISE TO
HAVE A DRINK WITH ME LATER.

23:26.970 --> 23:28.189
-I DON'T DRINK.

23:32.062 --> 23:33.586
WHY IS HE HERE?

23:33.716 --> 23:35.065
-BECAUSE I INVITED HIM.

23:36.197 --> 23:38.591
HE HAPPENS TO BE AN
EXCEPTIONALLY BRIGHT YOUNG MAN

23:38.721 --> 23:40.506
WHO IS STILL VERY
MUCH ENAMORED OF YOU.

23:40.636 --> 23:42.508
-AND STILL VERY MUCH A JERK.

23:42.638 --> 23:43.900
WHY DO YOU KEEP
DOING THIS TO ME?

23:45.728 --> 23:47.513
-BECAUSE I THINK YOU
CAN DO BETTER THAN EDDIE.

23:48.862 --> 23:50.298
SHAUNI, YOU COULD
HAVE ANYONE OF THESE

23:50.429 --> 23:52.866
PRODUCTIVE,
SUCCESSFUL YOUNG MEN.

23:52.996 --> 23:54.998
FOR THE LIFE OF ME, I CAN'T SEE

23:55.129 --> 23:56.957
HOW EDDIE STACKS UP
AGAINST ANY OF 'EM.

23:57.827 --> 24:01.527
-DAD, THIS IS NOT ABOUT
YOUR LIFE. IT'S ABOUT MINE.

24:01.657 --> 24:04.747
SO PLEASE, STOP TRYING
TO SABOTAGE IT, OKAY?

24:08.011 --> 24:12.059
[CROWD NOISES]

25:11.466 --> 25:13.033
-HEY EDDIE.
-HEY.

25:13.163 --> 25:14.382
-EDDIE, YOU CAME.

25:15.252 --> 25:16.297
SHAUNI WILL BE SO HAPPY.

25:17.124 --> 25:19.735
-I BROUGHT A LITTLE
GIFT FOR YOU AND GARY.

25:19.866 --> 25:20.997
-OH, HOW SWEET.

25:21.128 --> 25:22.521
THANKS, I'M SOAKED.

25:22.651 --> 25:23.957
CAN WE JUST PUT IT OVER THERE?

25:24.087 --> 25:25.349
THANKS.

25:33.793 --> 25:35.577
-SHE AROUND? YOU
KNOW WHERE SHE IS?

25:35.708 --> 25:38.188
-YEAH, I THINK SHE'S IN THE
HOUSE PUTTING ON HER SWIMSUIT.

25:38.319 --> 25:39.799
DID YOU BRING YOURS?

25:39.929 --> 25:41.017
-NAH. IT'S MY DAY OFF.

25:51.114 --> 25:52.463
-OH, I WANT YOU TO MEET GUS,

25:52.594 --> 25:54.770
HE STARTED WITH ME
OVER AT--

25:54.901 --> 25:56.424
-MR. MCCLAIN.

25:56.555 --> 25:57.773
-HEY, ROBERT IT'S
GOOD TO SEE YOU.

26:00.036 --> 26:01.211
-WANNA SHOW ME YOUR BEDROOM?

26:01.342 --> 26:02.212
-NO, I DON'T.

26:02.343 --> 26:03.605
-OH, COME ON.

26:03.736 --> 26:04.954
SHOW ME WHAT A GIRL WHO STILL

26:05.085 --> 26:06.782
LIVES WITH HER
PARENTS ROOM IS LIKE.

26:06.913 --> 26:09.698
BET THERE'S STUFFED
ANIMALS ALL OVER YOUR BED.

26:09.829 --> 26:11.221
-IF YOU DON'T LET GO OF ME,

26:11.352 --> 26:12.614
YOU'RE GONNA BE
A STUFFED ANIMAL.

26:12.745 --> 26:14.877
-AS LONG AS YOU
KEEP ME ON YOUR BED.

26:15.835 --> 26:17.271
NOW LET'S SEE THAT
PRETTY BATHING SUIT.

26:17.401 --> 26:19.012
-STOP IT, NOW!

26:20.709 --> 26:22.102
-WHAT DO YOU
THINK YOU'RE DOING?

26:22.232 --> 26:23.277
GET YOUR HANDS OFF OF HER.

26:24.321 --> 26:25.584
-CHILL OUT MAN.

26:26.585 --> 26:27.760
-YOU CHILL OUT.

26:29.239 --> 26:30.893
-EDDIE, COME ON. IT'S OKAY.

26:31.024 --> 26:32.721
I'M OKAY. IT'S OKAY.

26:35.071 --> 26:38.074
[COUGHING]

26:39.380 --> 26:40.686
-WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON HERE?

26:42.557 --> 26:44.472
-EVERYBODY, COME ON
INSIDE. WE'RE GOING TO

26:44.603 --> 26:46.692
TAKE GROUP PICTURES
IN FRONT OF THE HOUSE.

26:46.822 --> 26:48.389
NOW COME ON, LET'S GO.

26:48.519 --> 26:50.043
PICTURES WITH THE HAPPY COUPLE.

26:52.523 --> 26:54.221
KIM.

26:57.267 --> 26:59.966
NOW HONEY, WE CAN'T START
WITHOUT THE BRIDE TO BE.

27:00.096 --> 27:02.446
-THANKS.
-YOU'RE WELCOME.

27:04.448 --> 27:06.363
KIM, WHERE'S YOUR RING?

27:06.494 --> 27:07.800
-WHAT? OH GOD!

27:07.930 --> 27:09.410
-YOUR RING, IT'S
NOT ON YOUR FINGER.

27:09.540 --> 27:11.412
-IT MUST HAVE
SLIPPED IN THE POOL.

27:11.542 --> 27:12.892
-OH HONEY.

27:13.022 --> 27:14.458
-LOOK MOM, DON'T
WORRY, OKAY? I'LL FIND IT.

27:14.589 --> 27:15.634
YOU GO ON WITH THE GUESTS.

27:15.764 --> 27:16.852
-YOU SURE?

27:16.983 --> 27:17.810
-YEAH.
-OKAY.

27:19.594 --> 27:20.726
-BROWN STARTED IT.

27:20.856 --> 27:22.597
-I DON'T CARE WHO...

27:24.686 --> 27:28.168
I DON'T CARE WHO STARTED IT.
THIS IS AN ENGAGEMENT PARTY,

27:28.298 --> 27:29.691
NOT A PRIZE FIGHT.

27:29.822 --> 27:32.738
AND NOW FOR THE SAKE AND
THE SAFETY OF MY GUESTS,

27:32.868 --> 27:34.609
I HOPE YOU'LL BE GRACIOUS ENOUGH

27:34.740 --> 27:37.699
TO LEAVE THIS HOUSE AT ONCE,
AND TAKE YOUR PRESENT WITH YOU.

27:40.049 --> 27:41.877
-BROWN SHOULD BE
THE ONE TO LEAVE!

27:42.008 --> 27:43.749
-SHAUNI, FORGET ABOUT IT.

27:44.706 --> 27:46.099
I'LL CALL YOU LATER.

27:46.229 --> 27:51.234
[MELANCHOLY MUSIC]

28:08.425 --> 28:13.430
[SCREAMING]

28:18.305 --> 28:22.526
[OMINOUS MUSIC]

28:59.476 --> 29:02.653
-HELP! HELP!
SOMEONE CALL 911 NOW!

29:11.184 --> 29:12.272
-COME AHEAD EVERYONE,

29:12.402 --> 29:13.795
GET READY FOR THE PICTURES.

29:13.926 --> 29:15.623
GROUP PICTURES, RIGHT
OUTSIDE IN FRONT.

29:15.754 --> 29:17.233
GREAT, GOOD GOODY.

29:18.060 --> 29:19.670
-WHERE'S KIM?

29:31.552 --> 29:32.335
-TURN OFF THE PUMP.

29:32.466 --> 29:33.946
-WHAT?

29:34.076 --> 29:35.295
-TURN OFF THE PUMP. HER
HAND'S STUCK IN THE DRAIN.

29:35.904 --> 29:37.993
-TURN IT OFF NOW!
IT'S OVER THERE, GO!

29:38.124 --> 29:42.824
[OMINOUS MUSIC]

30:28.391 --> 30:29.349
-I GOT A PULSE.

30:29.479 --> 30:31.003
-CAPILLARY REFILL.

30:31.133 --> 30:32.831
-KIM!
LOOK OUT EDDIE!

30:32.961 --> 30:34.006
-GARY NO!

30:34.136 --> 30:35.137
-I'M A DOCTOR.

30:35.268 --> 30:36.835
-AND HE'S A LIFEGUARD.

30:43.842 --> 30:45.452
-COME ON.

30:45.582 --> 30:46.714
COME ON.

30:47.280 --> 30:48.716
COME ON.

30:50.979 --> 30:52.502
-EXCUSE US PLEASE.
WATCH OUT PLEASE.

30:52.633 --> 30:53.939
MOVE, PLEASE.

30:55.897 --> 30:57.464
KIMMY!

30:58.247 --> 30:59.248
-COME ON.

31:00.249 --> 31:01.381
COME ON.

31:09.737 --> 31:10.781
KIM.

31:10.912 --> 31:14.960
[COUGHING]

31:17.049 --> 31:18.789
-WHAT HAPPENED?

31:18.920 --> 31:20.748
-EDDIE JUST SAVED HER
LIFE. THAT'S WHAT HAPPENED.

31:20.879 --> 31:22.881
-DON'T MOVE,
DON'T MOVE, DON'T MOVE.

31:37.547 --> 31:38.592
-HEY HARVEY, LET'S GO.
-YEAH?

31:38.722 --> 31:40.159
-WHOA!

31:40.289 --> 31:42.726
-I'M SORRY. I'M SUCH A LOSER.

31:42.857 --> 31:44.250
-SHUT UP!

31:44.380 --> 31:45.512
-NO, I MEAN EVEN WHEN
I WIN I CAN'T WIN.

31:45.642 --> 31:46.687
-SHUT UP!
WILL YOU SHUT UP?

31:48.123 --> 31:48.907
COME ON.

31:49.037 --> 31:50.256
-WHERE?

31:50.386 --> 31:51.518
-TO PAY MR.
MYLES ANOTHER VISIT.

31:52.562 --> 31:54.521
-MYLES, WHAT FOR?

31:55.435 --> 31:57.350
-SINCE WE LEFT, SOMETHING'S
BEEN BOTHERING ME.

31:57.480 --> 32:01.267
DIDN'T HE SAY HE WAS WORKING
ON TWO IDENTICAL PROTOTYPES?

32:01.397 --> 32:02.442
-YEAH.

32:02.572 --> 32:04.096
-A PROTOTYPE IS ONE OF A KIND.

32:04.226 --> 32:05.619
-YEAH, YOU'RE RIGHT.

32:05.749 --> 32:07.447
-SO I HAD BEN CHECK
WITH SOME OF HIS PALS,

32:07.577 --> 32:09.275
SEEMS THAT MR. MYLES
DROPPED A BUNDLE

32:09.405 --> 32:11.930
IN A POKER GAME LAST
MONTH IN DEL MAR.

32:12.060 --> 32:16.543
-WAIT A MINUTE, VINCENT WON
BIG IN DEL MAR LAST MONTH.

32:16.673 --> 32:18.371
-MAYBE MR. MYLES
WAS JUST MAKING SURE

32:18.501 --> 32:19.633
HE GOT HIS MONEY BACK.

32:19.763 --> 32:25.160
[GENTLE MUSIC]

32:38.608 --> 32:40.393
-MYLES, WE WANNA TALK TO YOU!

32:44.266 --> 32:45.267
-STOP HIM!

32:52.753 --> 32:55.408
[FAST-PACED MUSIC]

33:11.337 --> 33:15.732
[SIRENS]

33:38.146 --> 33:40.105
-UNIT SEVEN PURSUING
AMPHIBIOUS VEHICLE

33:40.235 --> 33:42.324
AT TOWER TEN. CUT IT OFF.
DON'T LET IT GET TO THE WATER.

33:44.283 --> 33:48.156
[SIRENS]

33:48.287 --> 33:49.940
-UNIT
THREE RESPONDING.

33:50.071 --> 33:51.246
WE'RE RIGHT WITH YOU MITCH,
COMING IN FROM THE LEFT.

33:51.377 --> 33:55.120
[SIRENS]

34:26.672 --> 34:28.196
-RADIO THE
SCARAB TO CUT IT OFF,

34:28.327 --> 34:29.763
FORCE IT BACK TO SHORE.

34:45.692 --> 34:47.520
WE'RE HEADING NORTH ON
PCH TOWARDS THE CANALS.

34:47.650 --> 34:49.087
TRY TO FORCE IT OUT
OF THE WATER THERE.

34:58.183 --> 34:59.358
-THIS
IS BAYWATCH SCARAB.

35:00.446 --> 35:01.969
WE FORCED IT AROUND THE JETTY.

35:03.405 --> 35:05.494
IT'S HEADED TOWARDS SHORE
SOUTH OF THE CANALS.

35:05.625 --> 35:07.148
WE'LL TRY TO CUT IT OFF
AT THE MAIN CHANNEL.

35:07.279 --> 35:08.410
ON OUR WAY NOW, OVER.

35:14.329 --> 35:18.681
[ROCK MUSIC]

35:39.354 --> 35:41.922
-BAYWATCH HEADQUARTERS, I'VE
GOT THE AMPHIRANGER COMING IN.

35:42.052 --> 35:43.619
HEADING UP TOWARDS AVENUE 56.

35:56.893 --> 35:58.286
-IT'S ENTERING SUNRISE BAY,

35:58.417 --> 36:00.506
HEADING EAST TOWARD
THE CANALS. CUT IT OFF.

36:02.334 --> 36:06.990
[ROCK MUSIC]

36:48.597 --> 36:53.254
KMF 295 FROM UNIT SEVEN,
THE SCARAB IS IN PURSUIT,

36:53.385 --> 36:54.908
REQUEST BACK-UP AT
ALL CANAL EXITS.

36:55.038 --> 37:00.392
[ROCK MUSIC]

37:50.006 --> 37:52.705
IT'S HEADING SOUTH. I THINK
IT'S CIRCLING BEHIND YOU MITCH.

37:53.401 --> 37:54.968
-ROGER THAT HARVEY.

38:12.594 --> 38:14.161
STAY ON HIM!

38:14.857 --> 38:19.166
[PANTING]

38:53.548 --> 38:55.202
THAT'S MY WATCH.

39:00.773 --> 39:02.427
-SHAUNI, CAN'T WE TALK
BEFORE YOU DO THIS?

39:03.428 --> 39:04.951
-WHAT IS THERE TO TALK ABOUT?

39:05.081 --> 39:06.344
-THE CHOICE YOU'RE MAKING.

39:06.474 --> 39:08.694
-YEAH, IT'S MY
CHOICE AND I MADE IT.

39:09.216 --> 39:13.176
-SHAUNI, IF YOU'RE DOING
THIS JUST TO MAKE A POINT...

39:13.307 --> 39:16.876
-DAD, THE ONLY POINT IS THAT
I LOVE EDDIE, AND HE LOVES ME,

39:17.006 --> 39:18.312
AND WE WANNA LIVE TOGETHER.

39:18.443 --> 39:20.401
I'M SORRY IF YOU
DON'T APPROVE OF THAT,

39:20.532 --> 39:21.924
BUT I DON'T KNOW WHAT
ELSE HE HAS TO DO.

39:23.099 --> 39:24.449
-IT ISN'T THAT
I'M NOT GRATEFUL.

39:25.537 --> 39:29.671
GOD KNOWS HE SAVED MY DAUGHTER'S
LIFE, BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN

39:29.802 --> 39:32.326
I HAVE TO LET MY OTHER DAUGHTER
THROW HERS AWAY ON HIM.

39:35.503 --> 39:37.375
-I'M NOT THROWING
MY LIFE AWAY, DAD.

39:38.680 --> 39:39.855
YOU'RE THROWING IT AWAY,

39:41.596 --> 39:43.250
IF YOU DON'T LOVE
ME ENOUGH TO LET ME

39:43.381 --> 39:45.905
GO LIVE IT THE WAY I WANT TO.

39:50.518 --> 39:52.259
I WANT YOUR BLESSING.

39:58.613 --> 40:00.746
-I'M GONNA MISS YOU SHAUNI.

40:03.009 --> 40:04.402
-GOODBYE.

40:04.532 --> 40:09.885
[SOMBER MUSIC]

40:35.302 --> 40:36.782
-HOW YOU DOING? ARE YOU OKAY?

40:40.481 --> 40:42.570
-YEAH, I AM.

40:44.137 --> 40:46.356
LET'S GO.

40:50.796 --> 40:54.495
[ROCK MUSIC]

41:16.735 --> 41:18.476
-HE-EEY COME
ON, YOU'RE TELLING ME

41:18.606 --> 41:20.216
WE CAN'T USE ONE
OF THESE THINGS?

41:20.347 --> 41:22.305
CHECK IT OUT. IT'S
GOT EVERYTHING.

41:22.436 --> 41:27.093
IT'S GOT FOUR WHEEL DRIVE,
150 HORSEPOWER, A PROPELLER.

41:27.223 --> 41:31.401
IT'S GOT A MARINE COMPASS, A
FISH FINDER, AN ECHO SOUNDER,

41:31.532 --> 41:33.360
IT'S GOT A KILLER STEREO SYSTEM.

41:33.491 --> 41:36.319
HEY, ABOUT THE ONLY THING
IT DOESN'T DO IS TALK.

41:36.450 --> 41:37.233
-IT DOESN'T TALK?

41:37.364 --> 41:38.757
FORGET IT.

41:42.238 --> 41:45.546
[LAUGHING]

41:51.291 --> 41:55.817
[ROCK MUSIC]
